The paper discusses a system for detecting abnormal system behaviors for enterprise security, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The system uses a query language to express anomaly models and detect abnormal behaviors, which involves artificial intelligence techniques (cs.AI). The system also deals with large-scale monitoring data, which requires efficient data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). The system is designed for enterprise use, which involves software engineering practices (cs.SE). Finally, the system involves querying and analyzing data, which falls under the category of databases (cs.DB).
